hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections

Class LinkedListIndexedCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.Collection
      • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.LinkedListIndexedCollection

  • public class LinkedListIndexedCollection
extends Collection
    A linked list-backed collection of Objects. Duplicate elements are allowed. Storage of null references is not allowed.

    JJ
